name: metamorpha-point-cloud-dataset
description: This repository hosts a dataset of 609 point cloud files in .xyz format, obtained through white light interferometry (WLI). Accompanying the dataset is a .csv file that documents the laser parameters applied for each measurement. This dataset is part of the Horizon Europe Project METAMORPHA, focused on laser micromachining advancements.
